{
  "chapter": 18,
  "chapter_summary": "郭大路与燕七发现活剥皮鬼鬼祟祟地携带包袱出门，便强行搭上他的马车进城。途中活剥皮被迫打开包袱，里面仅有几件旧衣，其中一件是林太平的当品。二人花十两银子查看包袱后未发现端倪，但对活剥皮将林太平衣物带到城中的行为深感疑惑。马车抵达城中后，活剥皮将他们赶下车，前往一家客栈与两名神秘人接头——独臂人和刀疤大汉。原来这两人正在重金悬赏追捕林太平，活剥皮以五千两银子的价格出卖了林太平的线索。关键时刻，当铺中那位不起眼的烧饭老太婆突然现身，以惊世骇俗的武功轻松制服了独臂人，将活剥皮带走。郭大路与燕七由此得知老太婆竟是深藏不露的绝顶高手，对她为何甘愿在活剥皮当铺当老妈子的动机充满疑问。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "把门关上，千万不要放任何人进去，我明天早上才回来。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们想干什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "没什么，只不过想搭你的便车到城里去。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "不行，我这辆车说好了不搭人的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "不行也得行，我们既然已上了车，你难道还能把我们推下去？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "反正你本来就想请我们陪你去走一趟的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我找的不是你们……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "不是我们？你难道改变了主意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你们要搭车也行，只不过要出车钱。车钱一共是三钱银子，刚好一人出一钱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "燕七，我们打个赌好不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "好，赌什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我赌他这包袱里面有个老鼠，你信不信？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "不信。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "好，我跟你赌十两银子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你们不必赌了，我知道你们只不过想看看我这包袱，是不是？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "好像是有点这意思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "要看也行，看一看十两银子。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你们现在已觉得这十两银子花得太冤了吧？只可惜现在已收不回去了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "这包袱里有件衣服好像是林太平的，是不是？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "好像是吧，他反正已当给了我。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "当票还没有过期，他随时都可以去赎回来，你怎么能带走？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "他要赎的时候，我自然有衣服给他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "这件衣服他当了多少银子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "一两五钱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "好，我现在就替他赎出来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "不行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "有钱也不行？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "有钱还得有当票，这是开当铺的规矩，你有没有带当票来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "地头已到了，你们下车吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "你不要我们陪你逛逛吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "现在已用不着了，亲生子不如手边钱，能省一个总是省一个的好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "我们假如肯免费呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "免费更不行了，只要现金交易的生意，才是靠得住的生意，免费的事总是有点麻烦的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "那么我们就下车吧。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不送不送。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂人",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "不错，是他的衣服。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "text": "当然不会错的，在下做生意一向可靠。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂人",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "他的人在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂人",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "你现在就要？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "text": "开当铺的人都是现货交易，两位想必也知道的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，给他。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_ba_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "刀疤大汉",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "他在哪里你现在总可以说了吧？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "speaker_name": "活剥皮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你来干什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_huo_bo_pi",
      "text": "你吃药的时候已到了，为什么总是忘记呢？我特地替你送来，快喝下去吧。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂人",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "想不到阁下原来是位高人，好，好极了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "text": "不好，一点也不好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂人",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "有什么不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "text": "有什么好？你们遇见我，就要倒霉了，还有什么好？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂人",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "你究竟是什么人？敢来管我们的闲事？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "text": "谁管你们的事？你们的事还不配我来管，请我管我也不管，跪下来求我，我也不会管。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "独臂人",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "那么你来干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_du_bi_ren",
      "text": "我来要他吃药。快吃，吃完了药就该睡觉了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早就说过，你们的事就算跪下来求我，我也不管的，这人居然没听见，难道耳朵比我还聋么？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_ba_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "刀疤大汉",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "前辈，请等一等。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_dao_ba_da_han",
      "text": "还等什么？难道你也想来跟我磕个头不成？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_ba_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "刀疤大汉",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "前辈既然已伸手来管这件事，在下也没什么话好说，只盼前辈能留下个名号，在下等回去也好向主人交代。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_dao_ba_da_han",
      "text": "你想问我的名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dao_ba_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "刀疤大汉",
      "listener": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "text": "正想请教。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_dao_ba_da_han",
      "text": "你还不配知道我的名字，我说了你也不会知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_tai_po",
      "speaker_name": "老太婆",
      "listener": "char_dao_ba_da_han",
      "text": "但你却可以回去告诉你那主人，就说有个老朋友劝他，小孩子怪可怜的，最好莫要逼得太紧，否则连别人都会看不惯。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你坐下去的时候，难道从来也不看看屁股下面是什么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我没注意，我在想心事。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "我在想那老太婆，她明明是位很了不起的武林高手，为什么要在活剥皮的当铺当老妈子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "也许她也和风栖梧一样，在躲避别人的追踪。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "这理由乍一听好像很充足，仔细一想，却有很多地方说不通。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "世界这么大，有很多地方都可以躲避别人的追踪；尤其是像她这样的高手，为什么要去做别人的老妈子，听别人的指挥，受别人的气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "就算她要做人家的老妈子，也应该找个像样一点的人，找个像样一点的地方，为什么偏偏选上活剥皮？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你想不通？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "实在想不通。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你想不通的事，别人当然也一定想不通了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "若连我也想不到，能想通的人只怕很少。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "也许她就是要人家想不通呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "但想不通的事还有很多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "你说来听听。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "看她的武功，天下只怕很少有人能是她的对手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "她武功的确很高，我非但没有看过武功这么高的人，简直连听都没有听说过。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "所以我认为她根本就用不着怕别人，根本就用不着躲。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "莫忘记，强中更有强中手，一山还有一山高。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "speaker_name": "郭大路",
      "listener": "char_yan_qi",
      "text": "这只不过是句已老掉牙的俗话。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_qi",
      "speaker_name": "燕七",
      "listener": "char_guo_da_lu",
      "text": "老掉牙的话，往往是最有道理的话，越老越有道理。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 458
    }
  ],
